  <brief_title>Aripiprazole in the Treatment of Bipolar Depression</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 4 Study: An Open Prospective Study of the Safety and Effectiveness of Aripiprazole in the Treatment of Bipolar Depression</official_title>
